    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce traffic light system on products to rate/reward environmental impact",
        "additional_details": "The scores would be calculate using criteria such as - Land & Water Use, Air/Sea Miles, CO2, Sustainability, Ethical production, Packaging & for non consumables \u2013 end of life reuse.  Environmentally positive products should be tax free, those with a negative environmental impact taxed.  \r\n\r\nThis legislation would allow the consumer to make informed choices and add incentive to the manufacturers/suppliers to make their products less damaging.",
        "background": "Being a conscientious consumer is difficult when there are so many factors to consider.  The onus should be on the manufacturers /suppliers to let us know how ethical / environmentally sound their products are and they should be rewarded/reprimanded according to the environmental score applied.",
